It is possible to use the template in incorrect ways without producing error messages. <strong>[[#ombox|Please read the warnings and appropriate uses of this template at the beginning of the template description]].</strong>

* {{Nay}} <code>{{!mxt|{{tlf|Inflation/sandbox|UK|10|1971|5=fmt=eq}}}}</code> → {{!xt|{{Inflation/sandbox|UK|10|1971|fmt=eq}}}} (Omitting the {{para|cursign}} parameter will show the $ symbol by default, which is the wrong currency symbol for British currency)
* {{Aye}} <code>{{mxt|{{tlf|Inflation/sandbox|UK|10|1971|5=fmt=eq|6=cursign=£}}}}</code> → {{xt|{{Inflation/sandbox|UK|10|1971|fmt=eq|cursign=£}}}}
