* {{Nay}} <code>{{!mxt|$595 (${{tlf|Inflation/sandbox|US|595|1982|5=fmt=c}} in {{tlf|CURRENTYEAR}})}}</code> → {{!xt|$595 (${{Inflation/sandbox|US|595|1982|fmt=c}} in {{CURRENTYEAR}})}} (Misleading time reference)
