* {{Aye}} <code>{{mxt|$595 (equivalent to ${{tlf|Inflation/sandbox|US|595|1982|5=fmt=c}} in {{tlf|Inflation/year|US}})}}</code> → {{xt|$595 (equivalent to ${{Inflation/sandbox|US|595|1982|fmt=c}} in {{Inflation/year|US}})}}
